OL,5, Police Scotland has received more than 
OL,6, 3,000 hate crime reports since a new   
OL,7, law was introduced on Monday, the BBC  
OL,8, understands.                           
OL,10,FIt creates a new crime of "stirring up 
OL,11,Fhatred" over protected characteristics.
