OL,14,Fby First Minister Humza Yousaf - then  
OL,15,Fjustice secretary - highlighting white 
OL,16,Fpeople in prominent public roles.      
OL,18,FCommunity Safety Minister Siobhian     
OL,19,FBrown said people were making "fake and
OL,20,Fvexatious complaints".                 
